## ğŸ“– Overview

**Navam Invest** brings **institutional-grade portfolio intelligence** to individual retail investors managing $50K-$1M portfolios. Built on [LangGraph](https://langchain-ai.github.io/langgraph/) and powered by [Anthropic's Claude](https://www.anthropic.com/claude), it replaces traditional wealth management fees (1% AUM) with a team of **specialized AI agents** that collaborate through **multi-agent workflows** for equity research, systematic screening, macro analysis, earnings tracking, and portfolio managementâ€”all accessible through an interactive terminal interface.

