- âœ… **Live Status**: Real-time footer updates ("Processing..." â†’ "Ready")
- âœ… **Full Responses**: Increased max_tokens to 8192 (no more truncation)
- âœ… **Error Recovery**: Input always re-enables, even on errors

**Planned Features**:
- [ ] News Sentry agent (real-time event detection, 8-K material event monitoring)
